Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.45,0:03:45.87,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后我就迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,结果遇到了个这样的大叔
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,怪物
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.72,0:03:57.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,然后它说
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,用这个找路吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.16,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,把望远镜给我了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.30,0:04:07.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,哇~看的很清楚诶
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.64,0:04:13.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,掉到的篮子里有一个不认识的小哥
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个人是人贩子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.05,0:04:17.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们都是被拐卖的人
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.12,0:04:17.62,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.87,0:04:24.82,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我傍晚必须要给鸡喂食呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.08,0:04:28.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也是今天必须和父亲一起坐汽车回去
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.52,0:04:34.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我也是我也是 天黑之前不回去会出大事的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,会出什么大事呢
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.73,0:04:38.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,继续看吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.03,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大叔大叔
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.90,0:04:46.03,kono-text-cn-2,,0,0,0,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊 你往里看一下
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.74,0:04:52.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,一到晚上就会睡着的设定
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.91,0:05:04.35,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,让这家伙连晚饭也没得吃挺过意不去的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.19,0:05:08.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢了 浦野铃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.52,0:05:11.09,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你什么时候知道我的名字的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢了浦野铃
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,喂！ 别吵！
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.19,0:05:21.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我一定是犯迷糊了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.67,0:05:26.45,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,否则的话 那天的事一定是我的白日梦
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.81,0:05:35.86,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1444,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\bord0.1\blur5.019\pos(337,160.618)}1935
