Dialogue: 1,1:27:29.52,1:27:36.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60.232\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(384.095,262.298,499.36,294.855,0,3485)}羽毛谢谢了
Dialogue: 1,1:27:29.52,1:27:36.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60.232\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(301.314,350.75,419.249,385.979,0,3485)}谢谢你变得那么优秀
Dialogue: 1,1:27:29.52,1:27:36.48,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(941,0)\fn@方正毡笔黑_GBK\fs60.232\frz253.4\bord0\c&H85645B&\move(237.224,361.472,360.5,394.02,0,3485)}很高兴你能活着来看我
