Dialogue: 1,1:27:38.50,1:27:44.49,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs50.193\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,161.39)}1945
Dialogue: 1,1:27:38.50,1:27:44.49,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(303,211.583)}年
Dialogue: 1,1:27:38.50,1:27:44.49,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs60.232\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(331,310.505)}2
Dialogue: 1,1:27:38.50,1:27:44.49,kono-text-year,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1447,834)\fs70.27\fn@方正粗雅宋_GBK\frz270.8\c&HE7E5E5&\pos(303,351.345)}月
Dialogue: 1,1:27:46.66,1:27:48.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 鬼哥
Dialogue: 1,1:27:49.12,1:27:52.75,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是用那样一颗石子来代替尸骨
Dialogue: 1,1:27:53.50,1:27:55.50,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为太过小了 小澄竟然…
Dialogue: 1,1:27:55.46,1:27:58.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,鬼哥的…脑子？
Dialogue: 1,1:27:58.76,1:28:00.47,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,…这样搞混了
Dialogue: 1,1:28:00.84,1:28:02.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你哥哥是怎样的人
Dialogue: 1,1:28:03.55,1:28:06.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,大冷天的被叫过来 真傻
Dialogue: 1,1:28:06.39,1:28:08.89,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那个要一真的会这么容易死掉吗
Dialogue: 1,1:28:10.18,1:28:12.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真没劲 人总是突然消失了
Dialogue: 1,1:28:13.02,1:28:17.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,看不见身影了 就…没法传达话语了
Dialogue: 1,1:28:19.86,1:28:21.11,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,周作
Dialogue: 1,1:28:22.40,1:28:25.66,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,前段时间 谢谢你了
Dialogue: 1,1:28:27.08,1:28:30.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,给我时间和水原说话
Dialogue: 1,1:28:31.58,1:28:32.46,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没…
Dialogue: 1,1:28:33.21,1:28:34.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过 周作
Dialogue: 1,1:28:35.25,1:28:36.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夫妇是那样的吗
Dialogue: 1,1:28:38.88,1:28:41.84,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,因为是我硬要让你嫁过来
Dialogue: 1,1:28:44.09,1:28:46.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但你明明不表现给我看
Dialogue: 1,1:28:46.35,1:28:47.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样的生气表情
Dialogue: 1,1:28:47.97,1:28:48.72,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 1,1:28:49.14,1:28:50.85,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,现在不就在表现给你看吗
Dialogue: 1,1:28:52.73,1:28:55.10,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯~ 我倒是不知道你会生气
Dialogue: 1,1:28:55.52,1:28:57.31,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那是你注意力涣散而已
Dialogue: 1,1:28:57.86,1:28:58.98,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,嚯~
Dialogue: 1,1:29:00.73,1:29:03.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,所以你今天才穿了破洞的袜子
Dialogue: 1,1:29:04.41,1:29:07.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,是因为铃昨晚补的袜子我的脚穿不进去了
Dialogue: 1,1:29:07.95,1:29:09.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,也有别的袜子吧
Dialogue: 1,1:29:09.49,1:29:13.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,两位 这架必须得现在吵吗
Dialogue: 1,1:29:14.71,1:29:17.29,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,又走错路了 是这边
Dialogue: 1,1:29:17.29,1:29:18.54,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,1:29:19.00,1:29:22.30,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们家在那边 在那座灰之峰的方向
Dialogue: 1,1:29:22.38,1:29:23.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,都说了我知道
Comment: 0,1:29:24.16,1:29:25.99,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,#0
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.12,1:29:28.21,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小心火烛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.04,1:29:35.00,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,打败美英 小心火烛
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.34,1:29:40.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,在三天后
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.69,1:29:56.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不知道 这里没你找的那个人
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.83,1:30:14.04,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:30:17.00,1:30:20.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我们做这行的也不容易请多包涵
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.64,1:30:26.05,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你是为了自家男人来的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.35,1:30:27.76,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.73,1:30:32.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你听我解释
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.74,1:30:43.95,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是来给白木玲送东西的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:58.42,1:31:00.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我给你盛了点雪
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.67,1:31:04.51,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.76,1:31:07.55,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.81,1:31:14.27,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,味道真好
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.13,1:31:18.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我是来找白木玲的
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.61,1:31:25.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,玲的话 还在陪昨晚过夜的军官呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:30.87,1:31:35.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那样的话 能帮我把这只茶碗拿给她吗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.54,1:31:41.42,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,行啊行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.71,1:31:44.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊 这只茶碗
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.97,1:31:47.01,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,啊 你的手
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.84,1:31:50.56,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.76,1:31:53.02,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,有个年轻水兵用绳子缠住我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.10,1:31:55.39,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,打算拉着我一起跳进堺川（堺川：吴市外的一条河。）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:56.77,1:32:01.23,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没事 你别靠得太近 小心传染感冒
Dialogue: 0,1:32:01.65,1:32:03.78,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.94,1:32:05.57,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,反倒是你
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.41,1:32:08.91,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好凉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.57,1:32:12.20,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那么 那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.70,1:32:16.41,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那么小的河 怎么淹得死人呢（画面上的就是堺川）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.62,1:32:18.08,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你喜欢那个人吗
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.71,1:32:21.67,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,说喜欢也算喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.75,1:32:24.13,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但我并不是很了解他
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.55,1:32:29.68,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,前一阵子回来了不少军舰 店里生意好到不行
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.05,1:32:31.43,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.89,1:32:35.93,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,他看上去很绝望 我有上可怜他
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.23,1:32:41.52,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,夏天掉进河里还能舒服点
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.69,1:32:46.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,谁叫我特别怕冷呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.15,1:32:52.49,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,当初或许就该去温暖的南方
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.17,1:33:00.96,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.09,1:33:09.18,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,这种南方小岛好美
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.01,1:33:13.22,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.81,1:33:18.73,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.85,1:33:22.15,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,你好暖
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.36,1:33:26.90,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,天黑前我得把病养好才行
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.57,1:33:32.07,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,那我关窗了 別再把你冻着了
Dialogue: 0,1:33:46.71,1:33:50.88,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,家里 现在还很苦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.94,1:34:11.32,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,虽然我已经不再惧怕那些炮声了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.07,1:34:15.12,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,但是 周作
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.24,1:34:19.37,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己浑身上下都比不上玲
Comment: 0,1:34:22.41,1:34:26.33,kono-text-cn,,0,0,0,,#1
